snippet.title: The Count of Monte Carlo
snippet.description:
Available now, 'The Count of Monte Carlo' is a Blackjack RPG where both players and dealers twist the rules. Check it and the Blank Bundle out on the steam store!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1428980/The_Count_of_Monte_Carlo/
